    "data": [
        {
            "title": "福建8歲男童登山失聯逾120小時  千人晝夜搜1800米險峰未果",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"福建8歲男童登山失聯逾120小時。莆田新聞 / 極目新聞\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5b6a0c8050eaf5b1c1444454a7412bb3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050922110526259.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">福建8歲男童登山失聯逾120小時。莆田新聞 / 極目新聞</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近日，福建一名8歲男童在山上與父母走散，當地組織上千人進行搜救，但歷時5日仍未找到。\n\n</p><h2>尚未發現有效線索</h2>\n<p>福建莆田仙遊縣人民政府新聞辦9日通報稱，4日，該男童隨父母到仙遊縣石谷解登山，下山時與父母失聯。經多日搜尋，截至5月9日12時，搜救仍在進行中。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3438268/\">懸賞千萬︱深圳富豪尋回失蹤24年兒子 「我終於上岸啦」</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多部門開展救援行動。莆田新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5a1c22eedf70dc439abccc1f304e8c8b/2025-05/54095f8e704ff4bdd0c80ddcb372267.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多部門開展救援行動。莆田新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6e81b7c32dbd3100de47d77c038c04f/2025-05/602f497f1526d253cb02dede5ff188d.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1bdfe8266d87a81558b10c4dcc4acf7a/2025-05/a74979204f8d25a29cf56d6568367c9.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82dec6b401864a32da39b18460b20921/2025-05/41f3c8322020d27555236018dbfc689.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0fb055ab08a73fbdd7694b77e4d3c66d/2025-05/e7e5aedf2a76f0dc05bfc10109ac59c.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多部門開展救援行動。極目新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"走失男童。莆田新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3412a3d843ebad86bb1475d4323d07f2/2025-05/1b954c6eaee963bbe044af955353cd0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        走失男童。莆田新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>通報表示，4日16時左右，接到孩子母親的報警後，仙遊縣立即啟動應急響應機制，組織公安、森林消防、各地救援隊、志願者、鄉幹部及村民累計上千人次展開搜尋，並動用搜救犬和無人機熱成像等手段。由於石谷解海拔1803.3米，地形複雜，植被茂密，晝夜溫差大，連日雨霧，給搜尋帶來了很大挑戰。\n\n</p>\n<p>通報還稱，截至目前，救援人員尚未發現有效線索。仙遊縣將繼續開展搜救工作並擴大搜尋範圍。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3422393/\">雲南8歲女童雪山走失3天 父親懸賞100萬尋人</a></strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
