            "title": "麥潔文自嘲年紀大再爆身體有事或最後一次開騷  江華偕女兒任嘉賓收足歌酬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/afcac445478ccb9094c636baa0194e5b/2025-05/page_108.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/20ad3b5e2cd971f08d8036a5e8aa0102/7bfb2f1c738b4075bfe73a66f752c2d1-c30e5d0ff60965270f8189a096b6fe87-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681e0ad758c39\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681e0ad758c3b\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"麥潔文自嘲年紀大再爆身體有事或最後一次開騷  江華偕女兒任嘉賓收足歌酬\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5cee25ae494a6f3b77f81b262382d1a0/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050921264976464.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">麥潔文自嘲年紀大再爆身體有事或最後一次開騷  江華偕女兒任嘉賓收足歌酬</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>麥潔文「心動回眸」演唱會於本月21日在文化中心舉行，她與老公江華、女兒陳薔天早陣子綵排。麥潔文笑言未有安排一家人合唱，老公和女兒擔任嘉賓是老闆建議，又搞笑稱一定有酬勞。\n\n</p><h2>江華愛清爽光頭</h2>\n<p>70歲的麥潔文自嘲年紀大，可能是最後一次演唱會，「我望落後生，但擔心體力應付唔到，今次係挑戰自己。我患有先天性地中海貧血症，6年前做完演唱會後，人瞓醒都攰，晚上又瞓唔到。」麥潔文打算食補品養生，在旁女兒即大爆爸爸江華試過丟掉她的健康食品，江華解釋當時覺得年輕不用食。談到他身形Fit，江華說吃得清淡也不亂吃東西，人就會健康。提到他近年光頭示人，他說清爽，又認為要顧及髮型就有煩惱，現在沒有包袱。在旁太太即笑指：「佢似少林寺十八銅人。」陳薔天表示與媽媽同台演出多次，媽媽常分享舞台經驗，仍有壓力。對於會否跳唱演出？陳薔天稱信心不足。提到造型、服裝方面，麥潔文笑言與女兒有代溝，會同老公「夾夾」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240082/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"麥潔文與江華合唱，舉手投足見默契。 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35ed9f4acd6aa49bb6eefc133c88278a/2025-05/01_BUN_0688.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥潔文與江華合唱，舉手投足見默契。 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240083/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"麥潔文與老公江華、女兒陳薔天日前綵排。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/186b9433cdbc09f98b6988878ee7dadb/2025-05/02_BUN_0713.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥潔文與老公江華、女兒陳薔天日前綵排。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240085/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳薔天表示與媽媽同台演出多次，仍有壓力。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4e3f50a4ddae7b6967e68bff1e017ca9/2025-05/BUN_0658.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳薔天表示與媽媽同台演出多次，仍有壓力。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240125/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"麥潔文「心動回眸」演唱會於本月21日在文化中心舉行。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/201146b3cb1fdfa70cd3d0ca2b7bc6aa/2025-05/BUN_0673_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥潔文「心動回眸」演唱會於本月21日在文化中心舉行。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240126/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"夫妻情深對望與對唱。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/40c1e8511f9da70ff78a8ef8691ae351/2025-05/BUN_0679_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        夫妻情深對望與對唱。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240127/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"江華動作多多。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/91fb08d36ffb28bd258aa2a1f4ffdb78/2025-05/BUN_0686_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江華動作多多。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240128/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"麥潔文擔心體力不支，這次可能是最後一次演唱會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/705b7ee30b937db6a65b0671864572f1/2025-05/BUN_0702_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥潔文擔心體力不支，這次可能是最後一次演唱會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240129/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"麥潔文自嘲年紀大再爆身體出毛病。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb7fd578ee0d596105244bf243cc1f14/2025-05/BUN_0723_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥潔文自嘲年紀大再爆身體出毛病。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240131/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳薔天在2022年出道，想試吓跳唱風格。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e23dccdc73c953d61d1659e6359cf4d/2025-05/BUN_0729_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳薔天在2022年出道，想試吓跳唱風格。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240130/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\" 江華偕女兒擔任太太麥潔文演唱會的嘉賓，收足歌酬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4a5bee8cd14c19a8fd1b311babfd8b82/2025-05/BUN_0725_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         江華偕女兒擔任太太麥潔文演唱會的嘉賓，收足歌酬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240100/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"父親為女兒伴舞？\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9a6317fca26c892699e71274ae9c0050/2025-05/BUN_0741.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        父親為女兒伴舞？\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240101/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一家人接受訪問，充滿歡笑聲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/891c0bcf3798b6d3e87704b39de2ae24/2025-05/BUN_0747.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一家人接受訪問，充滿歡笑聲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
